<h3 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h3>
<p>Before we send you off to practice, we will look at one more “trick” one could do with integration by parts.  We will also illustrate a way to keep track of <span class="process-math">\(u\text{,}\)</span> <span class="process-math">\(\dx{v}\text{,}\)</span> <span class="process-math">\(\dx{u}\text{,}\)</span> and d <span class="process-math">\(v\text{.}\)</span></p>
